modName: Pretty Male and Female Mannequins - ADULT
descriptionHtml:
----------------------
Pretty Mannequins by Sandraniks
----------------------


ATTENTION! MOD CONTAINS NUDITY!


This mod replaces the default mannequins into pretty nude female ones.
Also I have added two extra mannequins - male and female - in Breezehome in Whiterun
Male mannequin also has been changed

I use UNP body replacer but I think the mod is compartible with all other replacers male and female 


Recommended mods

Pretty Female Idles by Dualsun http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/11954

Credits

VRDaphni who gave me the idea of this mod





--------------------
Installation
--------------------
Just drop all content from archive downloaded to your Skyrim Daya folder.
Activate SNPrettyMannequins.esp and play



-------------------
How to uninstall
-------------------
Just delete the esp.file from the Data folder



-------------------
Bugs
-------------------
Not detected so far




Feel free to reuse or reupload this file just give credits if you like it

Have fun!
author: Sandraniks
